cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for customer review analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of pre-trained language representations, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques for categorizing review aspects, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also discusses the use of active learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with customer reviews, which can be related to the category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
